ThemVet Claude Code Master Instructions

1. Purpose
This document is the master instruction file for Claude Code or any similar AI developer tool. It explains how to build ThemVet using the other files in this package.

2. Project Summary
ThemVet is a community-powered, AI-ready exam preparation platform for Indian competitive exams. It combines structured learning content, question practice, mock tests, community contributions, analytics, and AI assistance.

3. Recommended Reading Order
Claude should read the files in this order:
1. 00_ThemVet_README_Index.txt
2. 01_ThemVet_Business_Plan.txt
3. 02_ThemVet_Product_Spec.txt
4. 03_ThemVet_System_Architecture.txt
5. 04_ThemVet_Database_Schema.txt
